<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            border: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .cell {
            padding: 5px;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            min-height: 80px;
        }

        .cell:last-child {
            border-right: none;
        }

        .label {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: -1px;
        }

        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td.desc {
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Certificate of Origin</h1>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="cell">
            <span class="label">1. EXPORTER (Name and Address)</span>
            {{shipment.shipper.name}}<br>
            {{shipment.shipper.addressLine1}}<br>
            {{shipment.shipper.city}}, {{shipment.shipper.countryCode}}
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <span class="label">2. BLANKET PERIOD</span>
            FROM: {{date}}<br>
            TO: <br>(One year from today)
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <span class="label">3. PRODUCER (Name and Address)</span>
            SAME AS EXPORTER
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
            <span class="label">4. IMPORTER (Name and Address)</span>
            {{shipment.consignee.name}}<br>
            {{shipment.consignee.addressLine1}}<br>
            {{shipment.consignee.city}}, {{shipment.consignee.countryCode}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <table>
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>5. DESCRIPTION OF GOOD(S)</th>
                <th>6. HS TARIFF CLASSIFICATION #</th>
                <th>7. PREFERENCE CRITERION</th>
                <th>8. PRODUCER</th>
                <th>9. NET COST</th>
                <th>10. COUNTRY OF ORIGIN</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each shipment.lineItems}}
            <tr>
                <td class="desc">{{this.description}}</td>
                <td>{{this.htsCode}}</td>
                <td>A</td>
                <td>YES</td>
                <td>NO</td>
                <td>{{this.countryOfOrigin}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div style="border: 1px solid #000; border-top: none; padding: 10px;">
        <span class="label">11. I CERTIFY THAT:</span>
        <p>The information on this document is true and accurate and I assume the responsibility for proving such
            representations. I agree to maintain and present upon request, documentation necessary to support this
            certificate, and to inform, in writing, all persons to whom the certificate was given of any changes that
            could affect the accuracy or validity of this certificate.</p>

        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 30px;">
            <div style="width: 45%;">
                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">Authorized Signature</div>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 45%;">
                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">Company</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 20px;">
            <div style="width: 45%;">
                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">Name and Title</div>
            </div>
            <div style="width: 45%;">
                <div style="border-top: 1px solid #000;">Date: {{date}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>